data.description: Escape to your own piece of paradise with this serene 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home nestled on a 1.46-acre lot. Located just a short 15-minute drive from Fort Leonard Wood, this tranquil retreat offers the perfect blend of convenience & countryside living. Step inside  & be greeted by a warm & inviting ambiance, accentuated by the cozy gas fireplace in the spacious living room. The open floorplan creates an airy atmosphere, ideal for both entertaining guests. The heart of the home lies in the well-appointed kitchen, featuring a convenient breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances & ample cabinet space, making meal preparation a breeze. Outside, a spacious deck invites for outdoor gatherings in the expansive fenced-in yard. With meticulous maintenance & thoughtful design throughout, this peaceful home offers a harmonious blend of comfort, functionality & natural beauty. Don't miss the opportunity to make this idyllic retreat your own! Schedule a showing today!
